’Щ@dd3c9f373389498263610534d8f1ec212f30ae9569d5daa6fdd5423107d6b7e5Ъ?Title: title: polars expr-not
Path: Examples
Content:
Creates a not expression
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> (polars col a) > 2) | polars expr-not


```
Adds a column showing which values of col a are not greater than 2
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a]; [1] [2] [3] [4] [5]] | polars into-df
                    | polars with-column [(((polars col a) > 2)
                    | polars expr-not
                    | polars as a_expr_not)]
                    | polars collect
                    | polars sort-by a
